<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb7bc97df-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1992—<ref href="/us/pl/102/354/s3/b/2">Pub. L. 102–354, § 3(b)(2)</ref>, renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s587">section 587 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Subsec. (b). <ref href="/us/pl/102/354/s3/b/3">Pub. L. 102–354, § 3(b)(3)</ref>, substituted “section 573” for “section 583”.</p>
